Fixes #717 

There is a bug when AsyncRetryCenter init:
if delayRetryPolicy is null : 

-----

        if (delayRetryPolicy == null) {
            this.delayRetryPolicy = DelayRetryPolicy.newNoInitDelayPolicy();

           there lose a return:
            return;
        }
        this.delayRetryPolicy = delayRetryPolicy;

-----
